    <p>
      Report any sightings of Loggerhead Shrike in Ontario and Quebec, or shrikes with colour bands anywhere in North America to Wildlife Preservation Canada’s toll-free shrike line: 1-800-956-6608.  Be careful not to confuse Loggerhead and Northern Shrikes!  Northern Shrikes are present in the northern portions of the Loggerhead Shrike’s breeding range from September through March, when Loggerheads migrate south.
    </p>
